data.chText: 吉卜赛人（许多人更喜欢用Romany这个名称）
data.enText: a member of a race of people, originally from Asia, who travel around and traditionally live in caravans . Many people prefer to use the name Romany.

word_means: 吉卜赛人(许多人更喜欢用Romany这个名称)
自任骑士兼训练者的赛马马主

means: 吉卜赛人(许多人更喜欢用Romany这个名称)

value.def: A gypsy is a member of a race of people who travel from place to place, usually in caravans, rather than living in one place.

example.ex: ...the largest gypsy community of any country.
example.tran: 所有国家中最大的吉卜赛人族群
